        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer20751449" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4546267459188855513">CRAP CRAP CRAP...HATED IT!!! This is the epitome of nauseating travelogues. This woman thinks she is Italian because she renovated and lived in a small property in Tuscany??? And she is clearly so much smarter, knows better, and has more experience in everything (not JUST renovating and living in a small house in Tuscany) than anyone else on earth because she renovated and lived in a small house in Tuscany. Blech.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


