<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5568925582410670834">Frances Mayes&apos;s new book is <i> <b> See You in the Piazza: New Places to Discover in Italy </b></i>  published by Crown. Her most recent novel is <i> <b> Women in Sunlight,</b></i>  published by Crown and available in paperback in spring 2019. With her husband, Edward Mayes she recently published <i> <b> The Tuscan Sun Cookbook. </b></i>  <b>
  <i>Every Day in Tuscany </i>
</b> is the third volume in her bestselling Tuscany memoir series.<br/><br/>In addition to</span>
  <span id="freeText5568925582410670834" style="display:none">Frances Mayes's new book is <i> <b> See You in the Piazza: New Places to Discover in Italy </b></i>  published by Crown. Her most recent novel is <i> <b> Women in Sunlight,</b></i>  published by Crown and available in paperback in spring 2019. With her husband, Edward Mayes she recently published <i> <b> The Tuscan Sun Cookbook. </b></i>  <b>
  <i>Every Day in Tuscany </i>
</b> is the third volume in her bestselling Tuscany memoir series.<br /><br />In addition to her Tuscany memoirs, <i> Under the Tuscan Sun</i> and <i> Bella Tuscany </i>, Frances Mayes is the author of the memoirs <i> Under Magnolia: A Southern Memoir; A Year in the World</i>; the illustrated books <i>In Tuscany</i> and <i>Bringing Tuscany Home</i>; <i>Swan</i>, a novel; <i>The Discovery of Poetry</i>, a text for readers; and five books of poetry. She divides her time between homes in Italy and North Carolina. <br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="5568925582410670834" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

